Become a AI Machine Learning Engineer at 4Geeks Academy is a 16-week course that prepares students for a career in data science and machine learning. No previous knowledge is required. The course covers Python, SQL, Looker, Streamlit, and Statistics. Students will learn to create predictive models using Python libraries like Pandas and Numpy, and explore algorithms like Close Neighbors and Decision Trees. The course also focuses on solving real-life cases and developing AI projects from development to deployment and maintenance. Classes are held three times a week with a maximum of 12 students per class. The course offers certificates recognized by multiple organizations. No previous experience is needed, and students can choose between English and Spanish for the syllabus and content. For more information, visit the website: https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning. stop